-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ImageGap/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This is my second MacroGenics (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MGNX\" title=\"MacroGenics, Inc.\">MGNX</a></span>) article after 01/2023's \"MacroGenics: Uncertain Revenue Casts A Pall\" (\"<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4570170-macrogenics-uncertain-revenue-casts-a-pall\">Pall</a>\"). I rated MacroGenics as a (\"Hold\") in Pall. At the time of the article MacroGenics was trading at $5.32 with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185328417/image_185328417.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742428-macrogenics-biotech-with-growing-potential-still-not-a-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 23:00:33"}, {"id": "4742425", "title": "Enbridge: I Am Not Impressed With The Recent Dividend Increase", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1988673508/image_1988673508.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Abstract connections\" data-id=\"1988673508\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1988673508/image_1988673508.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1988673508/image_1988673508.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1988673508/image_1988673508.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1988673508/image_1988673508.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1988673508/image_1988673508.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1988673508/image_1988673508.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1988673508/image_1988673508.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1988673508/image_1988673508.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Enbridge Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ENB\" title=\"Enbridge Inc.\">ENB</a></span>) is a giant Canadian midstream company that boasts a network of pipelines, resource storage facilities, and other midstream infrastructure stretching across much of the United States and Canada:</p> <p></p> <p>As might be expected, this gives the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1988673508/image_1988673508.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742425-enbridge-i-am-not-impressed-with-the-recent-dividend-increase", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 22:48:15"}, {"id": "4742435", "title": "U.S. Bond Yields Rise As Reserve Currency Status Wanes", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038859/image_1436038859.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"The gold bond yield text and chart on Usa flag background 3d rendering\" data-id=\"1436038859\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038859/image_1436038859.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038859/image_1436038859.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038859/image_1436038859.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038859/image_1436038859.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038859/image_1436038859.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038859/image_1436038859.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038859/image_1436038859.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038859/image_1436038859.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">niphon/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Artis Shepherd</em></p> <p>With much consternation, capital markets participants are watching US Treasury bond yields go up while Jerome Powell and the Fed continue to lower the Fed Funds Rate in an effort to spur another</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038859/image_1436038859.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742435-us-bond-yields-rise-reserve-currency-status-wanes", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 22:45:00"}, {"id": "4742436", "title": "U.S. Bank Stocks Surge After Election To Highest Valuation Level In 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Little piggy banks on ascending stacks of coins\" data-id=\"1072593728\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5423px\" height=\"3261px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Investors bid up bank stocks following President-elect Donald Trump's victory in the 2024 presidential election. The rally was immediate and widespread, as the market expects less severe government regulation starting in 2025, including a more supportive regime for approving mergers</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742436-us-bank-stocks-surge-after-election-to-highest-valuation-level-in-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 22:36:00"}, {"id": "4742421", "title": "Bank of Montreal: Higher Credit Risks And A Higher Dividend", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/612615044/image_612615044.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Downtown Montreal Skyline at night\" data-id=\"612615044\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/612615044/image_612615044.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/612615044/image_612615044.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/612615044/image_612615044.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/612615044/image_612615044.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/612615044/image_612615044.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/612615044/image_612615044.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/612615044/image_612615044.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/612615044/image_612615044.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">NicolasMcComber</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Article Thesis</h2> <p>Bank of Montreal (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BMO\" title=\"Bank of Montreal\">BMO</a></span>) is a major Canadian bank with a compelling dividend growth track record. The bank's recent earnings results weren't strong, however, as higher credit loss provisions caused a profit shortfall. Shares have pulled back to some degree, but</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/612615044/image_612615044.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742421-bank-of-montreal-higher-credit-risks-and-a-higher-dividend", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 22:30:06"}, {"id": "4742416", "title": "Broadcom: Growth Prospects Don't Justify Current Valuation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1643360144/image_1643360144.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Broadcom headquarters in San Jose, California, United States\" data-id=\"1643360144\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1643360144/image_1643360144.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1643360144/image_1643360144.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1643360144/image_1643360144.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1643360144/image_1643360144.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1643360144/image_1643360144.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1643360144/image_1643360144.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1643360144/image_1643360144.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1643360144/image_1643360144.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Broadcom (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO\" title=\"Broadcom Inc.\">AVGO</a></span>) has performed phenomenally over the last year, returning over 80%. Fellow investors therefore might wonder if the company is still at an attractive entry point valuation-wise. In this article, we will first take a look at Broadcom's business as</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1643360144/image_1643360144.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742416-broadcom-growth-prospects-dont-justify-current-valuation", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 22:25:46"}, {"id": "4742289", "title": "Dorman Products: Kicking This Name Into Neutral", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94502433/image_94502433.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view of traffic and overpasses\" data-id=\"94502433\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5120px\" height=\"3413px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94502433/image_94502433.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94502433/image_94502433.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94502433/image_94502433.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94502433/image_94502433.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94502433/image_94502433.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94502433/image_94502433.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94502433/image_94502433.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94502433/image_94502433.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Northcut</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>One company for which things have been going pretty well for has been <strong>Dorman Products</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DORM\" title=\"Dorman Products, Inc.\">DORM</a></span>). For those not familiar with the firm, it operates as a major supplier of replacement and upgrade parts in the motor</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94502433/image_94502433.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742289-dorman-products-kicking-this-name-into-neutral", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 22:15:00"}, {"id": "4742433", "title": "Methode Electronics, Inc. 2025 Q2 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Methode Electronics, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q2 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106052\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742433-methode-electronics-inc-2025-q2-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 22:08:34"}]}